Code preview of the table C_楼层面积扣减设施类型表

drop table "C_DeductionFacilityType" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "C_DeductionFacilityType" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_DeductionFacilityType"
(
"FacilityTypeID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"FacilityTypeCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"FacilityTypeNameEN" VARCHAR2(20),
"FacilityTypeName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"DeductionType" INTEGER,
"CADCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_DEDUCTIONFACILITYTYPE primary key ("FacilityTypeID")
);

comment on column "C_DeductionFacilityType"."DeductionType" is
'人工输入参数面积扣减（例如：防火卷帘门扣减面积=长*宽，宽度为卷帘门两侧各加15cm以后的宽度）
图纸计算面积扣减（例如：消防栓扣减面积0.5平米）';

comment on column "C_DeductionFacilityType"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
